{
  "info": {
    "name": "Chatbot UPRIT — WhatsApp Webhook",
    "description": "Pruebas del webhook Meta WhatsApp y envío outbound vía Graph API.\n\nImporta también el environment `chatbot-uprit.postman_environment.json` y completa `webhook_secret` y `meta_token`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Health check",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": "{{base_url}}/health"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Webhook — Verificación Meta (GET)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{base_url}}/webhook?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token={{webhook_verify_token}}&hub.challenge=postman-challenge-123",
          "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
          "path": ["webhook"],
          "query": [
            { "key": "hub.mode", "value": "subscribe" },
            { "key": "hub.verify_token", "value": "{{webhook_verify_token}}" },
            { "key": "hub.challenge", "value": "postman-challenge-123" }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Simula la verificación que hace Meta al suscribir el webhook.\n\nRespuesta esperada: `postman-challenge-123` (texto plano, status 200)."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Webhook — Mensaje entrante simulado (POST)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "const secret = pm.environment.get('webhook_secret') || pm.environment.get('WEBHOOK_SECRET');",
              "if (!secret) {",
              "  throw new Error('Falta webhook_secret. Ejecuta: ./deploy/postman/sync-postman-env.sh y re-importa el environment en Postman.');",
              "}",
              "",
              "const waId = pm.environment.get('test_wa_id') || '51999888777';",
              "const text = pm.environment.get('test_message') || 'Hola, quiero información';",
              "const msgId = 'wamid.postman.' + Date.now();",
              "const ts = Math.floor(Date.now() / 1000).toString();",
              "",
              "const body = JSON.stringify({",
              "  object: 'whatsapp_business_account',",
              "  entry: [{",
              "    id: '1486400022400932',",
              "    changes: [{",
              "      field: 'messages',",
              "      value: {",
              "        messaging_product: 'whatsapp',",
              "        metadata: {",
              "          display_phone_number: '15550000000',",
              "          phone_number_id: pm.environment.get('phone_number_id')",
              "        },",
              "        contacts: [{ profile: { name: 'Usuario Postman' }, wa_id: waId }],",
              "        messages: [{",
              "          from: waId,",
              "          id: msgId,",
              "          timestamp: ts,",
              "          type: 'text',",
              "          text: { body: text }",
              "        }]",
              "      }",
              "    }]",
              "  }]",
              "});",
              "",
              "pm.variables.set('webhook_body', body);",
              "",
              "const signature = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(body, secret).toString(CryptoJS.enc.Hex);",
              "pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'x-hub-signature-256', value: 'sha256=' + signature });"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        },
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Meta espera 200 inmediato', function () {",
              "  pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{{webhook_body}}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "url": "{{base_url}}/webhook",
        "description": "Simula un mensaje de texto entrante de Meta.\n\nEl pre-request script:\n1. Arma el payload JSON oficial de Meta\n2. Calcula `x-hub-signature-256` con HMAC-SHA256 (WEBHOOK_SECRET)\n\nRespuesta inmediata: HTTP 200 (sin body). El bot procesa en background y responde por WhatsApp al número `test_wa_id`.\n\nRevisa logs en el servidor:\n`sudo docker compose -f /opt/chatbot-uprit/docker-compose.yml logs -f app`"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Meta Graph API — Enviar mensaje (outbound)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{meta_token}}" },
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"messaging_product\": \"whatsapp\",\n  \"recipient_type\": \"individual\",\n  \"to\": \"{{test_wa_id}}\",\n  \"type\": \"text\",\n  \"text\": {\n    \"preview_url\": false,\n    \"body\": \"Mensaje de prueba directo desde Postman (Graph API)\"\n  }\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "url": "https://graph.facebook.com/{{meta_api_version}}/{{phone_number_id}}/messages",
        "description": "Envía un mensaje directamente vía Meta Graph API (sin pasar por tu webhook).\n\nÚtil para verificar token y phone_number_id.\n\nEl número destino (`test_wa_id`) debe estar registrado como número de prueba en Meta Developers si la app no está en producción."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Webhook — POST sin firma (debe fallar 403)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"object\": \"whatsapp_business_account\",\n  \"entry\": []\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "url": "{{base_url}}/webhook",
        "description": "Prueba de seguridad: sin header x-hub-signature-256 debe retornar 403 Forbidden."
      },
      "response": []
    }
  ]
}
